NORTH ATLANTIC.
ANTIGUA TO UNITED KINGDOM.
12 METER VESSEL ORINOCO FLO, WHITE HULL, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
OVERDUE ANTIGUA (17-05N 061-48W) TO UNITED KINGDOM.
